<h2 id="instructions">Instructions</h2>

<p>Click anywhere on the screen to hide your cursor, and press the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">escape</code> key to show it again.</p>

<p>Use the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">arrow keys</code> to move around the environment.</p>

<p>Use the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">mouse</code> to look around the environment.</p>

<p>When your pointer becomes an open circle, click the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">left mouse button</code> to interact with the environment.</p>

